2 diagonal<br />\n之後三個terms係2*2*(4*2*2^12 + 6*2^2*2^8 + 4*2^3*2^4 + 2^4*1），即係有二連黑/白既情況<br />\n第一個overall predictor 2 係rotational symmetry ，既係打直睇一行定打橫睇一行，第二個係咩單數行1-2 group埋一行定2-3group埋一行。之後括弧入面係C 2^a*2^b ，C係揀邊一行做是2X8既行（即4Cr)，2^a係揀行既砌法，2^b係揀2X2 diagonal既砌法。睇第二個term 6*2^2*2^8，4行入面揀2行fix，所以4C2=6，2^2既係有兩個行可以點排（黑上白下再黑上白下、黑上白下再白上黑下，等等），2^8係剩低diagonal既case，個board得番2*4個2X2 blocks。<br />\n<br />\n我係咪諗得複雜左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb882819b90a44990c34ede18fc1fead0d7f584","tid":2361313,"uid":323922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a634874a0aca6384c103695bde65f2228c80e18b","tid":2361313,"uid":323922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T03:59:57.000Z","msg":"a) 我計到2^16 + 2^17 + 3*2^13+ 2^11+ 2^6<br />\n<br />\n第一個Term係全部2X2 diagonal<br />\n之後三個terms係2*2*(4*2*2^12 + 6*2^2*2^8 + 4*2^3*2^4 + 2^4*1），即係有二連黑/白既情況<br />\n第一個overall predictor 2 係rotational symmetry ，既係打直睇一行定打橫睇一行，第二個係咩單數行1-2 group埋一行定2-3group埋一行。之後括弧入面係C 2^a*2^b ，C係揀邊一行做是2X8既行（即4Cr)，2^a係揀行既砌法，2^b係揀2X2 diagonal既砌法。睇第二個term 6*2^2*2^8，4行入面揀2行fix，所以4C2=6，2^2既係有兩個行可以點排（黑上白下再黑上白下、黑上白下再白上黑下，等等），2^8係剩低diagonal既case，個board得番2*4個2X2 blocks。<br />\n<br />\n我係咪諗得複雜左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:02:09.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">Prefactor</span>"},{"pid":"82cdf872a0840a4a638d4f7967e023f181f26d2c","tid":2361313,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c8b2df734f4a2ac1e21053516cb9c9bf09315fc6","tid":2361313,"uid":121095,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"quote":{"pid":"abc39c3f5fcc0edb2962c4fd7c44e7f366e5790e","tid":2361313,"uid":3441,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"呢條係 combinatorics <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"Term黎姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:06:14.000Z","msg":"你咁撚求其 不如求其答算啦 第